ol\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|ITA]]<br><ref name=\"ita\">{{cite web | url=https://italiancharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Gemitaiz | title=Gemitaiz discography | website=italiancharts.com |accessdate=9 October 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br><ref name=\"swi\">{{cite web | url=http://hitparade.ch/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Gemitaiz | title=Gemitaiz discography | website=hitparade.ch |accessdate=9 October 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''L'unico compromesso''\n| 2013\n| 3 || {{spaced ndash}}\n| ITA: Gold\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Kepler''<br><small>(with MadMan)</small>\n| 2014\n| 1 || {{spaced ndash}}\n| ITA: Platinum\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Nonostante tutto''\n| 2016\n| 1 || 56\n| ITA: Platinum\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Davide''\n| 2018\n| 1 || {{spaced ndash}}\n| ITA: Platinum\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Scatola nera''<br><small>(with MadMan)</small>\n| 2019\n| 1 || 99\n| ITA: Platinum\n|}\n\n===EPs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\"| Peak positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Certification\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|ITA]]<br><ref name=\"ita\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Detto, fatto.''<br><small>(with MadMan)</small>\n| 2013\n| 24 \n| \n|}\n\n===Compilation albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\"| Peak positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Certification\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|ITA]]<br><ref name=\"ita\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''QVC Collection''\n| 2018\n| 27 \n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''QVC8''\n| 2018\n| 17 \n| \n|}\n